properties.Name: MineActivityItem
properties.Description:
Item(s) such as chemicals, material or other inventoried items consumed or produced by the mine activity.

Ex:
- Blasting caps
- Dynamite

Columns.Name: MineActivityId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a mine activity.

Columns.Name: ItemSku
Columns.Description: The Stock Keeping Unit identifier, which is typically used for inventory-related activities.

Columns.Name: MineActivityItemRelationshipTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a mine activity item relationship type.

Columns.Name: ItemUnits
Columns.Description: The units of the item consumed, produced etc.

Columns.Name: UnitOfMeasureId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Unit Of Measure.

Columns.Name: MineActivityItemNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the mine activity item.
